Package controller

Class DataController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.DataController
  • public class DataController
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is for business logic of School Admin Application.
    In this class we perform all the operations which are directly related to file.
    All the operations of fetching and removing from file or data formation for GUI class to use are contains in this class.

      • removeFromFile

        public void removeFromFile​(java.lang.String removeData)
        This is used to remove data from file.
        It will take the record string StudentCourse:courseId:studentId in this format and find in file and remove that line from file. Logic:
        We loop through each line of file and add the each line to one by one to new temporary variable except the removeData we get from method params. After completion of loop we replace file with temporary variable data.
        Parameters:
        removeData - This will be the string record which Admin wants to delte from file.

      • checkStudentExist

        public boolean checkStudentExist​(java.lang.String studentID)
        This is used to check if student is already exist in file.
        Logic:
        We go through each line of file and when we find keyword Student we compare that line studentId with params studentId if they are same we return true.
        Parameters:
        studentID - It will be studentId which is uniquely generated at creation time
        Returns:
        method will return true if already exist in file with same id otherwise false

        public boolean checkStudentAlreadyEnrolledInCourse​(java.lang.String courseId,
                                                   java.lang.String studentId)
        This method will use to check if student is already enrolled in given course.

        Parameters:

        preRequisite - Prerequisite courses require to enroll in this course

      • getCourseCurrentStudentCapacity

        public int getCourseCurrentStudentCapacity​(java.lang.String courseId)
        This is used to get the total number of enrolled students in the course. Logic:
        We go through each line of file and when we find keyword StudentCourse we compare that line courseId with param's courseId after that we check if course end date is not in past then we increase the count.
        Parameters:
        courseId - for which we have to find enrolled students
        Returns:
        will return the count of enrolled students
